<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Registration Rejection</title>
  <style>
    /* Global Styles */
    body {
      font-family: 'Arial', sans-serif;
      background-color: #f7f7f7;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
    }

    /* Container Styles */
    .container {
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 20px auto;
      padding: 20px;
      background-color: #ffffff;
      border-radius: 8px;
      box-shadow: 0px 0px 20px 0px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
    }

    /* Heading Styles */
    h1 {
      color: #dc3545; /* Red color for emphasis */
      text-align: center;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }

    /* Paragraph Styles */
    p {
      color: #555555;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
      line-height: 1.6;
    }

    /* Email Link Styles */
    a {
      color: #007bff; /* Blue color for links */
      text-decoration: none;
    }

    /* Signature Styles */
    .signature {
      font-style: italic;
      text-align: center;
      margin-top: 20px;
    }

    /* Responsive Styles */
    @media screen and (max-width: 600px) {
      .container {
        width: 90%;
        margin: 10px auto;
        padding: 10px;
      }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <h1>Registration Rejection</h1>
    <p>Hello <%= @employee.name %>,</p>
    <p>We regret to inform you that your registration request for the leave portal has been rejected.</p>
    <p>We appreciate your interest in accessing our leave portal. However, after careful consideration, we have determined that we are unable to approve your registration at this time.</p>
    <p>If you have any questions or require further assistance, please feel free to contact our support team at <a href="mailto:<%= @admin_email %>"><%= @admin_email %></a>.</p>
    <p>Thank you for your understanding.</p>
    <div class="signature">
      <p>Sincerely,</p>
      <p>Soft Coding Solutions</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
